## Access Control is a Commercial Feature

Access control has been enabled in the Stategraph configuration located in `.stategraph/config.yml`.

Access control is available in Stategraph's commercial offering. If you need role-based access control (RBAC), consider upgrading to a commercial plan.

For more details, visit our [pricing page](https://stategraph.com/pricing) or contact us at support@@stategraph.com.
